{"tid":1394760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[好鄰舍北區教會］我有啲肚餓想食飯又唔夠錢應該點做？","createTime":"2019-08-01T13:56:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T16:17:06.000Z","uid":251643,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a5080815048d96289051fdd81d99081075f1d733","tid":1394760,"uid":251643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:56:20.000Z","msg":"牧者以生命、行動去盡力行出「羊在牧在」<br />\n<br />\n走在街頭的不是他們的兒子，便可以視作等閒之輩嗎？他們都是上主所創造、所愛的，作為牧者與他們同行，就算偏袒他們又如何！因為高牆與雞蛋；玻璃與生命，大部分牧者都是站在雞蛋及生命的一方！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RgWFWac.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRgWFWac.png&h=a56ca051&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9z31FCE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9z31FCE.png&h=329de914&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申: 本人同「好鄰舍北區教會」無關係，純粹見到想俾巴絲們知道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">八月五號 全民罷工</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">時代革命 光復香港</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TnAfK7H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTnAfK7H.png&h=2744015e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7s0zgep.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7s0zgep.png&h=603d34f9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MjCay05.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMjCay05.png&h=d52b9875&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7iuz0F6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7iuz0F6.png&h=49e3dcd8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aF6Zsk8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaF6Zsk8.png&h=d0fce381&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vPjguzv.gif\" data-thumbna